The top recipe list is here! My most popular healthy recipes from 2024 – see if your favorite made the list!

As the year wraps up, I love diving into Google Analytics to see which recipes you enjoyed the most! These are the top recipes of 2024, based on your visits. It’s always fun to see which ones became the most popular. Did your favorite make the list?

Sorry I am late posting this, I know so many of you look forward to this list. It’s been another incredible year sharing recipes with all of you and getting your feedback. Some trends that are still here to stay, recipes with cottage cheese and high protein recipes. And, like every year all my chicken recipes and slow cooker recipes are always a hit.

I’m also rounding up links to my most popular posts from past years. If you’re new to Skinnytaste or just looking for inspiration to cook more in 2025, these TOP 25 recipes are a perfect starting point! I never got around to creating this list in 2018 and I apologize, but the yogurt bagel recipe for sure was number ONE! And although I started this blog in 2008, I didn’t start doing round ups until 2011. And if you’re new here, don’t miss my free weekly meal plans and high protein meal plans I share every Friday! Lastly, join the Skinnytaste What’s Cooking Community on Facebook for inspiration and dinner ideas to see what everyone else is cooking. Here’s to a happy and healthy 2025!
